==English==
===Noun===
{{wikipedia}}
'''stevia'''
# A [[sweet]] [[herb]], of [[genus]] ''[[Stevia]]'', native to [[Paraguay]]
# A [[sweetener]] extracted from this [[plant]] that can be substituted for [[sugar]] is some uses.  Much sweeter than an equal amount of sugar.

